# Stage 06 — review (L2)

Code review across 7 dimensions (correctness, security, performance, complexity, tests, docs, conventions) over what stage 04 delivered and stage 05 verified. P0/P1 issues trigger a fix loop (loopback to stage 04 — new wave or regeneration of existing wave). P2/P3 issues become tech debt recorded in `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.icm-main/docs/tech_debt.md` and the cycle proceeds to merge (07).

