## Gates

- **Human:** reviews `output/review-report.md`. If no P0/P1, approves "OK for 07?". If P0/P1, approves fix loop (automatic transition to 04).
- **Automatic (CI):** pre-commit hook validates L1↔outputs atomicity and commit prefix `workspace/{{WORKSPACE}}`.
- **Approval to transition:** human explicitly approves; sub_stage becomes `06_completed` in the commit that records the approval. Loopback to 04 does not require formal human gate — the reviewer classifying P0/P1 is sufficient; L1 transitions automatically.

## End of stage handoff (gate inline + 1-stage-1-session)

Stage 06 has two paths: loopback to 04 (automatic, no gate) and transition to 07 (with gate-inline). Bug v3.4.2 fixed only in Case A (transition to 07) — premature render+exit before approval created loop. Canonical doc: `<skill_root>/references/session-handoff-protocol.md`.

